textAfterTable: Interests Cooking Traveling Food Music Dancing Family Friends Hiking Mountain biking About Me Im a fun girl who wants someone to enjoy life with! My family means everything to me and would like to find someone that blends with my family....it should be effortless...i love my job and meeting new people everyday. I love to travel! I go to Austria every summer to visit my Oma, its like a second home for me and my sisters. I also do a lot of volunteer work for hospice patients. Its so rewarding to know I made someone's day just a little better. Always treat people the way you would like to be treated. I also love to cook and I'm definitely a feeder :). If you think we could be a match, please dont be shy...i dont bite :). First Date Dinner and/or drinks....cooking would be fun!
